                 <h1>How to Apply</h1>
				 <p>For all positions in Europe, the Middle East and Africa, you must apply through our online application system. Applications for graduate and internship programmes open in early September each year.</p>
                  <h2 class="questions">Making your application - General advice</h2>
                  <ul>
                  <li>Some business areas begin to interview before the deadline, so to avoid disappointment, please apply as early as possible</li>
                  <li>Make sure you research the industry, our company and your division of interest thoroughly</li>
                  <li>Check that you meet any minimum requirements</li>
                  <li>Only apply to one region, one office and one division</li>
                  <li>Take the time to decide where your skills and aspirations best lie</li>
                  </ul>

                   <h2 class="questions">What we look for</h2>
                   <p>Strong academic qualifications and quantitative skills are important for success in our programmes. Equally important are initiative, strategic and creative thinking, communication skills and a genuine interest in the financial markets.</p>
